data.description: Ten-minute drive to Edisto Beach!! This lovely home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths with approx.1800 sq ft on 1.99 acres of land+/-.Hardwood floors throughout home. Spacious living room and separate dining room with lots of natural light. Kitchen with plenty of cabinets and countertop space with recess lighting and also special lighting under top cabinets. A warm cozy Den off of the kitchen with knotty pine paneling. Master bedroom, two guest bedrooms with ceiling fans with reach in closets. Master bath has tile floors ,single vanity and shower. Hall bath with title large vanity, deep tub with shower. The backyard has lots of privacy with natural buffer including beautiful hardwood trees along both sides and back of property. Call for more details.
